Program: Outlook
Title: Outlook Weekend: The Gift
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/w3csvr1f
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 18 Dec 2017
Growing up in America Rob Scheer spent many years in foster homes. When he turned eighteen he received a dreary gift, but it inspires his work today. Alison Cope is the mother of the British Grime artist known as 'Depzman'. He bought her a designer watch from his first royalty cheque but in many ways it's a bittersweet gift. Image: man taking out rubbish in bags Credit: PhotoBylove Show less